INSERT INTO `cards` VALUES ('A1',1,'Bulbasaur','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_001_EN.webp','Narumi Sato','Mewtwo  pack','◊','Grass','Basic',NULL,70,'Fire','1','There is a plant seed on its back right from the day this Pokémon is born. The seed slowly grows larger.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',2,'Ivysaur','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_002_EN.webp','Kurata So','Mewtwo  pack','◊◊','Grass','Stage 1','Bulbasaur',90,'Fire','2','When the bulb on its back grows large, it appears to lose the ability to stand on its hind legs.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',3,'Venusaur','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_003_EN.webp','Ryota Murayama','Mewtwo  pack','◊◊◊','Grass','Stage 2','Ivysaur',160,'Fire','3','Its plant blooms when it is absorbing solar energy. It stays on the move to seek sunlight.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',4,'Venusaur ex','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_004_EN.webp','PLANETA CG Works','Mewtwo  pack','◊◊◊◊','Grass','Stage 2','Ivysaur',190,'Fire','3',NULL,1,NULL,NULL),('A1',5,'Caterpie','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_005_EN.webp','Miki Tanaka','Pikachu  pack','◊','Grass','Basic',NULL,50,'Fire','1','For protection, it releases a horrible stench from the antenna on its head to drive away enemies.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',6,'Metapod','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_006_EN.webp','Yuka Morii','Pikachu  pack','◊','Grass','Stage 1','Caterpie',80,'Fire','2','It is waiting for the moment to evolve. At this stage, it can only harden, so it remains motionless to avoid attack.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',7,'Butterfree','https://limitlesstcg.nyc3.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/pocket/A1/A1_007_EN.webp','Shin Nagasawa','Pikachu  pack','◊◊◊','Grass','Stage 2','Metapod',120,'Fire','1','In battle, it flaps its wings at great speed to release highly toxic dust into the air.',0,NULL,NULL),('A1',8,'Weedle','https://limitlesstc